Bola Tinubu, a chieftain of the All Progressives Congress (APC), met with traditional rulers in Oyo state on Sunday. Tinubu has been meeting and consulting with key stakeholders as part of activities before formally declaring his intention to contest the number one seat in the country. As part of his consultation tour, the former Lagos governor met with Lamidi Olayiwola Adeyemi, the Alaafin of Oyo, and Lekan Balogun, the Olubadan designate. See pictures below. <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-665306" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/IMG-20220220-WA0015-1024x682.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="599" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-665304" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/IMG-20220220-WA0017-1024x682.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="599" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-665305" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/IMG-20220220-WA0016-1024x682.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="599" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-665323" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/WhatsApp-Image-2022-02-20-at-17.49.55-2.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="481" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-665324" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/WhatsApp-Image-2022-02-20-at-17.49.55-1.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="481" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-665325" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/WhatsApp-Image-2022-02-20-at-17.49.55.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="481" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-665321" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/WhatsApp-Image-2022-02-20-at-16.55.51.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="540" />